				<ul>
					<li>Dog Towels</li>
					<li>FoamCare Shampoo and Conditioner</li>
					<li>Cordless Professional Clippers</li>
					<li>Magic Coat Brush</li>
					<li>Stainless Steel Nail Clippers</li>
					<li>Deep Cleaning Pet Wipes</li>
				</ul><br><br>
				
	
			<p>With these products you can groom your pet at home with our helpful tips.  Before you begin, make sure you have the correct equipment including drain covers or sprayers to help prevent drain clogs and help clean your pets.  Next, try to remove excess hair with a brush before getting your pet wet.  Use shampoo and conditioner to remove dirt and then rinse and dry your pet.  Next you can use clippers to trim your pet's hair.  Between baths use wipes to get rid of dirt on the coat.</p>
		
